\section{Introduction}
The system is a program designed to manage utility consumption in this case water consumption for either domestic or commercial meters. The system is called ``HAVEN PREPAID WATER SYSTEM''. It enters the amount of money paid by a customer or user and calculates the number of units for the amount paid.

\section{System Constants and Conditions}
The program required authentication and some fixed values for calculations. These values of constants are listed below:
\begin{itemize}
    \item \textbf{System Access PIN:} 4545
    \item \textbf{Fixed Maintenance Fee Deducted:} 500.0 UGX
    \item \textbf{Domestic Unit Rate:} 150.0 UGX per Unit
    \item \textbf{Commercial Unit Rate:} 250.0 UGX per Unit
    \item \textbf{Leakage Alert Safety Limit:} 50.0 Units per day
\end{itemize}

